{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>After having a bad day at work you decide to go for a nice and relaxing trip to the newly opened cozy cove mini golf resort, but something is not quite right.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359900/extras/putt.gif?t=1723948614\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The game </h2>Gone Golfing is a first person golfing game that combines multiple elements from eldritch horror to comedy slashers. <br>Not only will you have to play golf, you will also have to survive and solve puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359900/extras/fish.gif?t=1723948614\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Physics Based Golfing<br></li><li> Survival Horror with enemy AI that will hunt you<br></li><li> Unique Puzzle Solving<br></li><li> Deep story with multiple endings<br></li><li> Surreal environment, combining Lovecraftian horror with 80's slashers<br></li><li> Crazy golf mascots<br></li><li> Mutated zombie trouts with legs<br></li><li> Unlockable Escape Mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Includes three DLC expansions</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Merry Golfmas DLC</h2>You return Cozy Cove, but things have changed.<br>It's colder, darker and even the rules have changed. <br>You have five attempts to escape so make them count.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Merry Golfmas Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> New map<br></li><li> New rules ( five attempts to escape )<br></li><li> New puzzles<br></li><li> New Achievements <br></li><li> Christmas themed enemies </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Golfmare DLC</h2>You wake up in a house that seems familiar yet different. <br>Solve puzzles and try to escape the horrors of your past.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Golfmare Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> New location<br></li><li> New puzzles<br></li><li> New Achievements <br></li><li> New enemies </li></ul><h2 class=\"